entity
{
	"id" "52718"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "We ve met before. In the emptiness of the beginning. Just dont say you forgot."
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_start"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "72 -2616 688"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52720"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Have you noticed? Everyone here has found their own corner. Stanley has music, the narrator has a dispute with the writer, you have..."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_corner1"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "72 -2800 648"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52722"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Different paths. The illusion of choice. And I have paper and endless data."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_corner2"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "72 -2800 664"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52724"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Its a party. Only there are no guests... But since you dropped by, it means I wasnt waiting in vain."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_party"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "50 -2736 648"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52726"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "You know, a writer is not a person. It is just a shell.... Underneath it is the shining Archaean, the twelve-dimensional pattern... You have already seen it in its lair."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtverkisto"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "0 -2696 648"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52728"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "When he spoke as a human, the words were simple. As if everything was better before, the grass was greener."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtverkisto2"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "0 -2696 664"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52730"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "When he was Archei, these were formulas, dunes, landscapes... Incomprehensible to us..."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtverkisto3"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "0 -2696 680"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52732"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "I tried to save both forms of it. But the paper tears and the codes break. Parts always get lost."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtverkisto4"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "0 -2696 696"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52734"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Youve heard him. He loves the settings more than the game itself, he stores everything, records everything. Thats why they called him: Settings Person."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-39.4973 -2755.68 648"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52736"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "In the first centuries he was sane. But after eight billion years.. the numbers ate away at his mind."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator2"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-38 -2756 664"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52738"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "After 'Epilogue', 8 billion years ago... He didnt stop. Sequel after sequel. Each time a new shell for the old voice."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator3"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-40 -2756 680"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52740"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "When he talks about the future, his eyes are empty. He does not see the present."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator4"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-41.3552 -2755.02 696"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52742"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "And the writer... He looks back. He longs for his 2D version, when the game was flat and honest."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator5"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-43.7158 -2753.5 712"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52744"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "He despises updates. For him, sequels are betrayal. When the Narrator creates, he breaks."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator6"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-46.1128 -2754.23 728"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52746"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Theyre like poles. One always running forward, the other always pulling back."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator7"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-53.2571 -2754.71 648"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52748"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "Eight billion years of fighting. And neither one had the courage to admit the other was right."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator8"
	"x" "-1"
	"y" "0.85"
	"origin" "-52.5505 -2754.74 664"
	editor
	{
		"color" "220 30 220"
		"visgroupshown" "1"
		"visgroupautoshown" "1"
		"logicalpos" "[3000 -5268]"
	}
}
entity
{
	"id" "52750"
	"classname" "game_text"
	"autobreak" "1"
	"channel" "1"
	"color" "100 100 100"
	"color2" "240 110 0"
	"effect" "0"
	"fadein" "1.5"
	"fadeout" "0.5"
	"fxtime" "0.25"
	"holdtime" "8"
	"message" "And Im just an archiver. Im just 'Obsolete Guy'. I write reports. I keep their fights in drawers and folders."
	"spawnflags" "0"
	"targetname" "obselete_guy_abtnarrator9"
	"x" "-1"
